<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="description"
              content="sbomify access request rejected notification">
        <meta name="keywords" content="sbomify, access, rejected, notification">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Your Access Request Has Been Rejected</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
            }
            .rejection-notice {
                background-color: #fff3cd;
                border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
                padding: 15px;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Your Access Request Has Been Rejected</h1>
        <p>
            Hello
            {% if user.first_name %}{{ user.first_name }}{% endif %}
            ,
        </p>
        <div class="rejection-notice">
            <p>
                Your request for access to gated components in the workspace <strong>{{ team.name }}</strong> has been rejected.
            </p>
        </div>
        <p>If you would like to request access again, you will need to sign the NDA again as part of your new request.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions about this decision, please contact the workspace administrators.</p>
        <p>
            Best regards,
            <br>
            The sbomify Team
        </p>
    </body>
</html>
